snippet.title: NOWAYFARER
snippet.description:
(//‿•)🤘🏻 Hi there! This is Nowayfarer 🥰 🎸 Welcome to my channel. I'm a self-taught guitar-playing guy –with bleached blond hair–  from Paris 🇫🇷 (France) and film with my very own camera equipment 📸 some events from time to time in Paris, London 🇬🇧, and all around Europe 🇪🇺.
ALL CONTENTS ARE 100% MY OWN. All the videos shown on this channel have been filmed by MYSELF at a variety of festivals, gigs and events.  Feel free to subscribe to get all the latest videos.
For all press related inquiries, video licensing or commercial filming including drone photography requests, 
please email: nowayfarer@gmail.com

IF YOU TAKE ANY OF MY CONTENT WITHOUT PERMISSION I WILL TAKE YOUR VIDEO DOWN
